==English==

===Etymology===
From [[Ancient Greek]] ''{{polytonic|ποιέω/ποιῶ}}'' (poiéo/poió), meaning ''I create/make/do/cause''.

===Noun===
{{en-noun-unc}}

# the class of [[literature]] comprising [[poems]]
# composition in verse or language exhibiting conscious attention to patterns

